{"tid":2368466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三度攤大手板 涉160億公帑","createTime":"2021-01-16T08:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:27:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d7c7f7f770e99161ff84f3e48e094901e624a9","tid":2368466,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:22:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/GIGQ4CYTXBAMLHUVU2S45LRXUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FGIGQ4CYTXBAMLHUVU2S45LRXUI%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyHbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=46d4a7d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FGIGQ4CYTXBAMLHUVU2S45LRXUI%2F&h=1b69d089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/GIGQ4CYTXBAMLHUVU2S45LRXUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n三度攤大手板 涉160億公帑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VZTxBJcX0yElG_Se-gWw1j07huI=/3093x1740/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UOUGDVGXZRB6DAGHL5DBLRZOKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVZTxBJcX0yElG_Se-gWw1j07huI%3D%2F3093x1740%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUOUGDVGXZRB6DAGHL5DBLRZOKI.jpg&h=82c749f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港珠澳大橋近年嚴重超支淪為大白象工程，連同昨日申請的主橋工程，港府已就港珠澳大橋主體及配套工程三次向立法會申請追加撥款，涉款合共接近160億港元。為配合港珠澳大橋工程，港府2011年成功向立法會申撥162億元興建大橋香港接線，翌年再向立法會提出追加撥款，涉及約89億港元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：運房局申追加撥款  港珠澳橋再超支貼15億 建制盲撐：世紀工程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通車逾兩年 流量從未達標<br />\n<br />\n港府當年向立法會提交文件解釋，大橋本地工程受司法覆核程序影響而延遲約九個月，動工時間變得非常緊逼，須增加資源確保工程順利進行，因此希望向立法會申請追加撥款。承。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一配套項目是大橋香港口岸設施，2011年已獲批304億元，四年後港府又向立法會攤大手板，追加55億元。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋經多次延遲及超支後終於2018年10月通車，惟用量遠低於預期。根。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"c63e1682baf01c56caefe0662518d9c21c3aa4b1","tid":2368466,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"炸左佢好過啦"}]}